title: Javon "Wanna" Walton joins the show!
description:
The man known as "Ashtray" from Euphoria, Javon "Wanna" Walton pops into the show, to talk about his new project, "Samaritan" where he plays the side-kick to an aging superhero, as well as his love of boxing (2-time national silver medalist), and his experience as the iconic "Ash." The guys also get into the Deshaun Watson situation, break down what we should take away from the settlement between the NFL and NFLPA, and GM Jalen finally accepts a deal for Kevin Durant! Pop the trunk with us.
